Prescription Drug Benefits Take advantage of our many pharmacy plan options
Allow us to personalize your benefit offerings to best meet the needs of you and our employees

What are prescription drug benefits? We offer many pharmacy plans and services. This allows us to personalize our products to best meet the needs of you and your employees Work with us to take advantage of our integrated and stand alone pharmacy plan options, strategic pharmacy account management; mail order and specialty pharmacy services, competitive rates, negotiated discounts with participating pharmacies, and rebates:
We offer strong clinical programs to keep costs down. These programs include:
Managed Pharmacy Program Our prescription drug plans give members access to more than 57,000 national and independent participating pharmacies to get your prescriptions filled:

Online & Phone Order (Tel-Drug) Ordering prescriptions either online or by phone through Tel-Drug is a convenient alternative to a retail pharmacy. Members will experience prompt; confidential delivery to their home or other preferred location.
Special Programs for Middle Market, Large Enterprises & Health & Wellness Trust Funds Innovate Healthcare offers specialized pharmacy programs that help manage pharmacy costs

Individual & Family Plans Our Individual and Family Plans offer a simple-to-use, comprehensive health plan design to provide you and your family with the comfort and peace of mind that comes with dependable health coverage:

Contact us Innovate Healthcare agent to find out how we help you get valuable coverage at an affordable Contact your price Evans at devans@lnnovate.com Fore more information about the Innovate Healthcare Group Insurance product, please contact David or (614) 555-1212.
